    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Attacking
    Represents an abstract class for attacking plants in a game.
    AudioManager
    The AudioManager class provides static methods to control background music playback within an application.
    Basic
     
    Board
    Represents the game board in a tower-defense style game such as Plants vs.
    Brainstein
    The Brainstein class represents a specific type of entity in the game that extends functionality from the Generate class.
    Buckethead
    Represents the Buckethead zombie character, which is a type of zombie with high hit points, capable of moving across the game board and attacking plants.
    Cell
    Represents a single cell in a game grid.
    Character
    Represents a character in a game with basic functionality such as health management.
    Conehead
    Represents a Conehead zombie in the game.
    Defensive
    The Defensive class is an abstract subclass of Plant that serves as a blueprint for creating defensive plant types in a game.
    ECIPlant
    ECIPlant is a specialized type of Support plant.
    ECIZombie
    Represents a specialized type of zombie called ECIZombie, which is a child class of the Movement class.
    Evolve
    Represents an advanced attacking plant in the game that evolves from the basic attributes provided by the Attacking class.
    Game
    Game crepresents the graphical user interface for the Player vs Player game.
    GameManager
    The GameManager class is responsible for managing the game's state, resources, and interactions in the Player vs Player mode.
    GameManagerMIvsMO
    The GameManager class is responsible for managing the game's state, resources, and interactions in the Machine vs Machine (PlantsIntelligent and ZombiesOriginal) mode.
    GameManagerMIvsMS
    The GameManager class is responsible for managing the game's state, resources, and interactions * in the Machine vs Machine (PlantsIntelligent and ZombiesStrategic) mode.
    GameManagerMSvsMO
    The GameManager class is responsible for managing the game's state, resources, and interactions * in the Machine vs Machine (PlantsStrategic and ZombiesOriginal) mode.
    GameManagerMSvsMS
    The GameManager class is responsible for managing the game's state, resources, and interactions in the Machine vs Machine (PlantsStrategic and ZombiesStrategic) mode.
    GameManagerPvsMO
    GameManagerPvsMO is responsible for managing the game's core functionality in the Player vs Machine (ZombiesOriginal) mode.
    GameMIvsMO
    The GameMIvsMO represents the graphical user interface for the Machine vs Machine (PlantsIntelligent and ZombiesOriginal) game.
    GameMIvsMS
    GameMIvsMS represents the graphical user interface for the Machine vs Machine (PlantsIntelligent and ZombiesStrategic) game.
    GameMSvsMO
    The GameMSvsMO class represents the graphical user interface for the Machine vs Machine (PlantsStrategic and ZombiesOriginal) game.
    GameMSvsMS
    GameMSvsMS represents the graphical user interface for the Machine vs Machine (PlantsStrategic and ZombiesStrategic) game.
    GamePvsMO
    GamePvsMO represents the graphical user interface for the Player vs Machine (ZombiesOriginal) game.
    GamePvsMS
    The GamePvsMS class extends JFrame and serves as the main class for creating a game interface.
    Generate
    The Generate class is an abstract subclass of Zombies, designed for entities that possess the ability to generate "brains" as resources in the game.
    Movement
    Represents a zombie with movement capabilities in the game.
    Pea
    Represents a projectile, typically used as an attack or defense mechanism in the game.
    Peashooter
    The Peashooter class represents a specific type of attacking plant in the game.
    Plant
    Represents a plant in a game, such as a strategy or tower defense game, that inherits from the Character class.
    PlantsMachines
    PlantsMachines is a GUI application class that extends JFrame.
    POOBvsZOMBIESException
    Represents custom exceptions specific to the POOBvsZOMBIES game.
    PotatoMine
    PotatoMine is a type of defensive plant with explosive capabilities.
    Select
    The Select class represents a graphical user interface for selecting game modes in the POOBvsZOMBIES application.
    Shovel
    The Shovel class represents a tool used for digging or moving materials such as soil, sand, snow, or coal.
    Start
    The Start class represents the introductory window for the POOBvsZOMBIES application.
    Sunflower
    Represents a Sunflower plant in the game, which is a type of support plant.
    Support
    The Support class is an abstract extension of the Plant class, designed to represent a type of plant in the game that generates sunlight at regular intervals.
    WallNut
    WallNut is a defensive plant in the game with high durability.
    ZombieMachines
    The ZombieMachines class represents the main window for the "POOBvsZOMBIES (PlantsMachines)" game.
    ZombiePlantSelector
     
    Zombies
    Represents an abstract Zombie entity within the game.
